company.taskMan.task

Class OriginalTaskProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • company.taskMan.task.OriginalTaskProxy

  • public class OriginalTaskProxy
extends java.lang.Object
    An OriginalTaskProxy is a local placeholder for a remotely delegated task. It has a reference to the task that is delegating (delegatingTask) to update it about remote changes. The only connection to the remote branch happens through the DelegatingTaskProxy which is located in the remote branch. All communication between this proxy and the actual delegated task runs through the remote DelegatedTaskProxy.
    Author:
    Tim Van Den Broecke, Vincent Van Gestel, Joran Van de Woestijne, Eli Vangrieken
